author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Weingarten Realty Sees 2018 Disposition Volumes Similar To 2017​
text:
Jan 25 (Reuters) - Weingarten Realty Investors:
* WEINGARTEN REALTY INVESTORS - ‍ANTICIPATES THAT DISPOSITION VOLUMES FOR 2018 COULD BE SIMILAR TO 2017​
* WEINGARTEN REALTY INVESTORS - ‍INVESTED $124 MILLION IN NEW DEVELOPMENTS AND REDEVELOPMENTS IN 2017 AND EXPECTS TO SPEND A SIMILAR AMOUNT IN 2018​
* WEINGARTEN REALTY INVESTORS - ‍WRI ANTICIPATES THAT DISPOSITION VOLUMES FOR 2018 COULD BE SIMILAR TO 2017​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
